# Review Checklist

## Product clarity

- [ ] Is the main user clear?
- [ ] Is the problem clear?
- [ ] Is the expected output clear?

## Engineering clarity

- [ ] Is the CLI interface clear?
- [ ] Are modules separated?
- [ ] Is file generation deterministic?

## Testing

- [ ] Is input parsing tested?
- [ ] Is output directory behavior tested?
- [ ] Is overwrite protection tested?

## Scope control

- [ ] No LLM API in v0
- [ ] No GitHub integration in v0
- [ ] No web UI in v0
- [ ] No configurable workflows in v0